OL,7,FInflation rates have slowed to 6.8%
OL,8,Fin July, down from 7.9% in June, that
OL,9,Fmeans prices are still going up, but
OL,10,Fjust not as much as they were, as ITV
OL,11,FNews Correspondent Lucy Watson
OL,12,Fexplains
OL,14,FInflation slowed to its lowest for 17
OL,15,Fmonths in July due to a fall in
OL,16,Fenergy prices and a slowdown in food
OL,17,Fprice increases, according to
OL,18,Fofficial figures.
